(e) fleeting or negligible; or
(f) in an advertisement or commercial announcement for a work described in this subsection (7)
(8).
(9)(9) No civil action may be maintained under the provisions of this section unless it is commenced
within 4 years after the party seeking to bring the claim discovered, or should have reasonably discovered, the
